<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Xinput on DjangoZane</title><link>https://blog.djangozane.com/tags/xinput/</link><description>Recent content in Xinput on DjangoZane</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-Hans</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2019 13:05:56 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.djangozane.com/tags/xinput/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>禁用笔记本的自带键盘</title><link>https://blog.djangozane.com/post/%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%B8%A6%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2019 13:05:56 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.djangozane.com/post/%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%B8%A6%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;最近半年笔记本的键盘已经慢慢地开始失灵，经常有些键按不出来，所以就另外买了一把键盘。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不过有时候需要带笔记本出去，所以这样一来还需要带着键盘，为了在把键盘放在笔记本的自带键盘上不会误触到就决定禁用掉自带键盘。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>